0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:04:57.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"3a5fce8768e5b11e1c05b17941a8f920e7401771","tid":1555294,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:38:37.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266c99220b2a66bcf8516ab2dcc5a1485b57c576","tid":1555294,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeab6e1282c4a4ff62e58074eb6c2b0e50d445b0","tid":1555294,"uid":26876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"如發現被自殺者有性暴力痕跡<br />\n一定會入示威者數"},{"pid":"f4a4c623f0ca7e6952bcef30d0605da0148a342c","tid":1555294,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"Agree 推爆佢"},{"pid":"b7d1f736a1da0a418399fd6602c774a2240c9061","tid":1555294,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:54:21.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"fc18a5fafc3a8d6ab872adb15e274cec10817686","tid":1555294,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"承襲英國法系的香港設有「太平紳士」（Justice of the Peace，或稱治安法官）制度，分為官守、非官守和新界太平紳士，由政府委任資深政府官員、熱心公益事務人士，或對香港社會貢獻良多者擔任，職責之一為巡視監獄等羈押場所，接受被拘留者投訴，以免他們遭受法院判決以外之刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n一名太平紳士直言，新屋嶺扣留中心這類設施是監督上的「盲點」，他強調「我們不是去判斷被扣留者有沒有罪，而是確保他們受到人道對待」。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該寫信搵佢地入去新屋嶺？"},{"pid":"2f740ab9e84c52557589abb6861e67c2977526e2","tid":1555294,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:17:54.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"3d2eaf0e3932fe259f6333bfe74bb63e0d65dd49","tid":1555294,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34cc7d4584f6a6ea5cb0d60d9d0a9c14c82ed696","tid":15